  "title": "RESINOUS SHATTERING EGYPTIAN STROP BAKE",
  "description": "A sweet and sticky weeknight Egyptian dish made with dutch stroop, perfect for a quick dessert or snack. This recipe is free from onions and garlic for those who can't handle them.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
